---
const title = "About Me";
---

<style>
  section {
    display: flex;
    position: relative;
    flex-direction: column;
    text-align: center;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    font-family: var(--font-family-intro);
    color: var(--color-text-default);
  }

  .about-container {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    color: var(--color-text-default);
    margin: 0 var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .about-title {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xxl);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .about-text {
    width: 50%;
    font-size: var(--font-size-md);
    text-align: justify;
    padding: 0 var(--spacing-lg);
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .about-text p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-image {
    right: var(--spacing-lg);
    width: 50%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .about-image img {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-xl);
    width: 50%;
    transform: rotate(10deg);
    border-radius: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .about-image img:hover {
    transform: rotate(5deg) scale(1.1);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-title {
      font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    }

    .about-container {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0 var(--spacing-lg);
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .about-text {
      width: 100%;
      font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
      text-align: justify;
      padding: var(--spacing-sm);
      order: 2;
    }

    .about-image {
      width: 100%;
      order: 1;
    }

    .about-image img {
      max-width: 40%;
      width: auto;
      height: auto;
      transform: rotate(0deg);
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    .about-image img:hover {
      transform: scale(1);
    }
  }
</style>

<section id="about">
  <p class="about-title">{title}</p>
  <div class="about-container">
    <div class="about-text animate-fade-in">
      <p>
        Hi, I'm Yixuan. <br /><br />
        Born in China 🇨🇳, I've studied in the UK 🇬🇧 and Germany 🇩🇪, and now I'm based
        in Zurich, Switzerland 🇨🇭. I'm into all things tech—from Natural Language
        Processing to web development and 3D modeling. I've taught myself tools like
        Blender, Astro, and Three.js, and I'm always experimenting, breaking things,
        and figuring out how to put them back together (better). <br /><br />
        Outside the screen, you'll probably find me traveling 🛥️, cycling 🚴🏻‍♀️, playing
        badminton 🏸, or out hunting Pokémons :P I love exploring - both the world
        around me and the things I don't know (yet).<br /><br />
        Right now, I'm focused on becoming a better developer. I've been documenting
        my journey as I go, hoping that my learning process might help others starting
        out too. <br /><br />
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-image animate-fade-in">
      <img src="/me.jpg" alt="About Me Image" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
